  <brief_title>Endoscopic Versus Radiologic Biliary Drainage for Perihilar Malignant Obstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Efficacy and Safety of Endoscopic Biliary Drainage and Percutaneous Transhepatic Biliary Drainage for the Management of Perihilar Malignant Biliary Obstruction: a Monocentric Retrospective Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
