  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This retrospective monocentric study aims at comparing multimodality endoscopic biliary&#xD;
      drainage versus percutaneous radiologic biliary drainage in case of perihilar malignant&#xD;
      obstruction.&#xD;
&#xD;
      Data from patients admitted in the Nancy University Hospital, France, between january 2016&#xD;
      and march 2022 with jaundice and perihilar obstruction will be retrospectively collected.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
